---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Ecosystem">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Ecosystem</p>
      <h1>One platform for NFTs, SocialFi, and GameFi.</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Fozeus connects digital ownership, community reputation, and playable assets into a coherent
        Web3 experience powered by the FZS token.
      </p>
      <div class="grid gateway-grid">
        <article class="card"><h3>1. NFT Collections</h3><p>Create, trade, and collect unique digital assets with verifiable scarcity and on-chain provenance.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>2. SocialFi Layer</h3><p>Turn community engagement into owned reputation and tokenized rewards across Web3 social graphs.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>3. GameFi Mechanics</h3><p>Build play-to-earn experiences where in-game assets are real NFTs with cross-platform portability.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>4. AI Integration</h3><p>Leverage AI-powered tools for asset generation, community moderation, and on-chain agent experiences.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>5. FZS Token Utility</h3><p>Use FZS for governance, staking, in-game rewards, and premium ecosystem access.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>6. Metaverse Ready</h3><p>Design assets and experiences that travel across virtual worlds and open metaverse platforms.</p></article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .gateway-grid {
    margin-top: 42px;
  }
</style>
